  "title": "Record-only commit lane for task ledger maintenance",
  "status": "running",
  "milestone": "RFT-M5",
  "dependencies": [],
  "acceptance": [
    "Add an official `node atm.mjs git record-commit` lane.",
    "The lane must not require a task-bound session.",
    "The lane must require explicit actor identity and a commit message.",
    "The lane must fail closed when staged files are empty or include non-record paths.",
    "The lane must reject closure packets, protected override audit, and repair-like evidence metadata so high-risk boundaries keep using their dedicated governed surfaces.",
    "Same-commit `git-head` provenance must still be staged when governed ledger boundary files are committed.",
    "Help/spec and focused regression coverage must describe the new lane.",
    "Backlog row `ATM-BUG-2026-07-08-058` must be closed with validator evidence."
  ],
  "deliverables": [
    "packages/cli/src/commands/git-governance.ts",
